      "index": 0,
      "indent": 0,
      "text": {
        "en": "Talk to Explorer Jack who is located in a house west of the Lumbridge General Store. (opciones de chat: 2 You mentioned a quest? • Accept • 1 How do I get to the Land of Snow? • 3 Actually, never mind.)",
        "es": "Habla con Explorer Jack, que se encuentra en una casa al oeste de la Lumbridge General Store. (opciones de chat: 2 You mentioned a quest? • Accept • 1 How do I get to the Land of Snow? • 3 Actually, never mind.)"
      }
    },
    {
